snippet.description:
#titanic #timotheechalamet #zendaya 

A story across time.

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @KHStudio please subscribe:
✅ YouTube: https://bit.ly/KHstudio

🎥 Attention viewers!

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. I have meticulously incorporated various effects, sound design, AI technologies (Google Veo 3), movie analytics, and other elements to bring my vision to life. Its purpose is purely artistic, aiming to entertain and engage with the YouTube community. My goal is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through this trailer. Thank you for your support, and let's dive into the world of imagination! 🍿

Software I use: Adobe Premiere, After Effects, Photoshop, Adobe Audition, Mocha Pro
------------------------------------------------
▶️ Watch More:

Interstellar 2 - https://youtu.be/6W6XMvYH0Xs

Edward Scissorhands - https://youtu.be/TKkn-qTDsEM

Titanic 2 - https://youtu.be/9tNWfBoqWrU
------------------------------------------------
🚢 Titanic 2 

A century after the real-life disaster and over 25 years after James Cameron’s Titanic broke box office records, a new generation is about to experience the legendary romance and tragedy — this time with a fresh twist. Rumor has it that a reimagined version of Titanic is in the works, with Timothée Chalamet and Zendaya set to star as star-crossed lovers aboard the ill-fated ship.

The project, tentatively titled Titanic, is said to be less of a straight remake and more of a “reinterpretation” — blending historical drama, romance, and a modern narrative structure designed to resonate with younger audiences while honoring the grandeur of the original film.

Insiders claim that this new Titanic will weave together two timelines: the doomed 1912 voyage and a present-day investigation by a young historian (played by Zendaya) uncovering a mysterious diary linked to a passenger named Jack Dawson — here reimagined and played by Timothée Chalamet.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: Crowd Stops in Awe as 4-Year-Old Sings ‘Goodness of God’
snippet.description:
When Karolina Protsenko introduced her 4-year-old brother Nicholas to the crowd, no one expected what happened next. Nicholas sat at the piano and began to sing Goodness of God with such pure emotion that the crowd stopped in awe.
Some started singing along, others just stood still — many said they had never experienced anything like it. 🎹 Goodness of God cover by 4-year-old Nicholas Protsenko and his sister Karolina is a truly beautiful moment of sibling harmony, worship, and talent.

✨ Watch as this street performance melts hearts and inspires everyone who hears it.

snippet.title: Good Boy - Official Trailer | HD | IFC Films
snippet.description:
Indy, a loyal golden-brown retriever, follows his owner Todd to an aging farmhouse tucked deep in the countryside. But the walls whisper, the shadows breathe, and something unseen has already claimed the place. Todd is blind to the horrors curling around them — but Indy can see. Through the dog’s eyes, the world twists into a nightmare of flickering visions and lurking shapes. Bound by unshakable loyalty, Indy stands between his human and the darkness, ready to face the things no one else can see.

Concept Trailer

It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Victor Valverde x JR Torres - El Mayor de Los Ranas (LETRA)
snippet.description:
📌¡Muchas gracias por ver nuestros videos !! espero te haya gustado. ✨

🔔 ¡No olvides activar las notificaciones para mantenerte al tanto de nuestros nuevos vídeos!

▶️ Te invitamos a ver el vídeo oficial aquí, si aun no lo has hecho !!
https://youtu.be/Af1U4FmM1S4

📝 Letra/ Lyrics:

Se miran zumbando en alr patrullando
puro kamikaze y nomás el terror sembrando
de arriba p'abajo, ahí nos miran patrullando
cero tolerancia para el que la ande cagando
ya se las sabrita' que no nos gustan las fallas
la gorra de lado y la glockson viene eclipsada
con un toque bueno y a punta de carcajadas
afirma pendientes, nunca se nos pasa nada
la santa protege si salimos a topones
y al cien con los jefes, estamos a la puta orden
pa morir nacimos, siempre estamos a la orden
y uno de lavada si salimos a misiones
y ahí nos ven pasar
zumbando los ranas por el bulevar
y el aparato en mano y el tostón atrás
y el mayor de los ranas siempre al frente va
en uno y al tentón
quedó comprobado la vez del jefe ratón
que vamos de fresa, no tenemos compasión
a punta de tostonazos traíamos el boludón
y así nomás, compa junior torres, viejillo
pura doble v
nos miran placosones encortados, el aparato a un lado
con un toque bueno y un perico de lavado
sabandijas y ratas en corto los alineamos
yo los amarro
y se siente el ambiente caliente
yo voy al frente con mi gente
nunca me gusta mandar gente
y se siente el ambiente caliente
si el blindado va hasta el frente
sembrando el terror como siempre
y ahí nos ven pasar
zumbando los ranas por el bulevar
y el aparato en mano y el tostón atrás
el mayor de los ranas siempre al frente va
en uno y al tentón
quedó comprobado la vez del jefe ratón
que vamos de fresa, no tenemos compasión
a punta de tostonazos traíamos el boludón
